      <title>俄罗斯石油制裁意味着中东原油价格创下多年来新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/russian-oil-sanctions-mean-mideast-crude-is-strongest-in-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于争相购买受制裁的俄罗斯石油的替代货物，中东原油价格已较全球基准价格出现异常溢价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/russian-oil-sanctions-mean-mideast-crude-is-strongest-in-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 14:37:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
