      <title>阿布扎比 Eagle Hills 计划斥资 60 亿美元开发佐治亚州项目，力争实现全球扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/abu-dhabi-s-eagle-hills-plans-6-billion-georgia-projects-in-global-push</link>
