      <title>纽蒙特以 4.25 亿美元的价格将加拿大金矿出售给 Discovery Silver</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/newmont-sells-canadian-mine-to-discovery-silver-for-425-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽蒙特公司 (Newmont Corp.) 将以高达 4.25 亿美元的价格出售其位于安大略省的 Porcupine 金矿，该公司在收购 Newcrest Mining Ltd. 后完成了资产剥离计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/newmont-sells-canadian-mine-to-discovery-silver-for-425-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 13:40:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
